title: The Foundry Hotel
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Italian, Western, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Classic Victorian pub in Golden Square. Has a small separate veg menu containing around 6 vegan and 10 vegetarian items - ask for it when you go in to order. Gives 10% off evening meals if you order before 6:30pm. Parking is behind the pub, on Old High St or just park at the Woolworths car park.
